description:
Oh Joy, this week's Honest Trailer is Inside Out 2! How do you succeed in the Anxiety-ridden state of today's cinemas? A Disgust-ing amount of sequels of course! Pixar let Fear decide to leave original concepts in the past, and if that makes your Anger rise, stay Envy-ous, loser, because this made an Embarrassment of riches!
